Aikiconnect Training Program

Aikiconnect nig.ltd is a professional and experienced body that manages trainings/workshop sessions aimed at improving system and human capacity development. The target audience includes individuals seeking self-improvement through knowledge, training, and human capacity development, as well as businesses looking to train their staff in public financial management.
